\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle \sigma\right\rangle =\frac{\lambda}{3!}\left\langle \phi_{a}\phi_{a}\right\rangle \sim g\hat{v}^{2}\sim\mathcal{O}\left(1\right)$
\end_inset

